column16: Ryan Hanigan lines into a double play, right fielder Jason Heyward to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.   Ian Desmond doubled off 1st.
Ian Desmond singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Ian Happ.
Carlos Gonzalez grounds into a force out, third baseman Kris Bryant to shortstop Javier Baez.   Mark Reynolds out at 2nd.
Mark Reynolds singles on a ground ball to left fielder Kyle Schwarber.
Nolan Arenado lines out to left fielder Kyle Schwarber.
DJ LeMahieu called out on strikes.
Charlie Blackmon homers (14) on a fly ball to right field.    Chris Rusin scores.
Chris Rusin singles on a soft ground ball to shortstop Javier Baez.
